  "texts": [
    "Finally, MobMess identified 1,169 plasmid systems, which together represent 1,169 backbone and 63,926 maximal clusters (3,255 maximal clusters were excluded).",
    "See Supplementary Fig. 3 for a diagram of these numbers.",
    "We ran MobMess separately on the 16,827 reference plasmid sequences, yielding 11,121 clusters.",
    "We assumed that all reference plasmids were circular and thus, there were no fragment clusters.",
    "We visualized networks with Cytoscape 94 v3.8 and laid nodes out using the prefuse directed force layout 95."
  ],
